ASK_USER=AskUserQuestion
ASK_USER_OTHER_NOTE=(AskUserQuestion adds it automatically)
SKILLS_DIR=~/.claude/skills
RULES_DESCRIPTION=`.claude/rules/*.md`, `CLAUDE.md`, plus explicit language and codestyle rules
RULES_LINE_1=1. **`.claude/rules/*.md`** — all rule files (Glob `**/.claude/rules/*.md`)
RULES_LINE_2=2. **`CLAUDE.md`** — root and nested (Glob `**/CLAUDE.md`)
RULES_LINE_3=3. **`docs/plans/*-design.md`** — approved design documents when plan or compliance review needs them
RULES_SOURCE=`.claude/rules/*.md` and `CLAUDE.md`
DISPATCH_AGENT=Launch reviewers in parallel using Agent tool with `subagent_type="code-reviewer"` and `run_in_background=true`. Send all Agent calls in a single message for true parallelism.
INVOKE_SKILL=Use the Skill tool to invoke the target skill directly.
PROGRESS_TOOL=TodoWrite
FILE_DISCOVERY=For file discovery, use Glob, Grep, or MCP filesystem tools if available. Do not fall back to shell commands (find, grep) unless no dedicated tool is available.
